reviewText: An intelligently written movie! I love indie movies that manage to be refreshingly well done, a lot of them just aren't any good. This one made me glad I took the gamble & bought it.
Porcelain Man reminded me of a movie I saw back in the day that I can't for the life of me remember the title of. It was good though and this is too. Worthy of your time
This movie has a really cool concept. I've seen similar stuff but I think the producers put their own mark on this . Check it out, I certainly enjoyed it.
